<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">

  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
    }

    header {
      background: #e63bc7;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .container {
      width: 80%;
      margin: 30px auto;
      max-width: 1000px;
    }

    .about-section {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .about-section h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .team {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .team-member {
      background: #e7f5f0;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .team-member:hover {
      border: 2px solid gray;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      border-color: rgb(93, 212, 238);
    }

    .team-member img {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-bottom: 0px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 2px solid rgb(225, 52, 222);
    }

    .pof {
      margin-top: -10px;
      padding-top: 0px;
    }

    .team-member h3 {
      margin-top: 0px;
      margin-bottom: -5px;
    }

    footer {
      background: #e63bd2;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    /* Modal Styles */
    .modal {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      z-index: 1000;
      padding-top: 100px;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      overflow: auto;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }

    .modal-content {
      background: white;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      width: 400px;
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

    .modal-content img {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 2px solid #3be6aa;
    }

    .close {
      color: red;
      float: right;
      font-size: 25px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.9);}
      to {opacity: 1; transform: scale(1);}
    }
.social-icons {
  margin-top: 15px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 20px;
}

.social-icons a {
  color: #3be6aa;
  font-size: 24px;
  transition: transform 0.2s, color 0.2s;
}

.social-icons a:hover {
  color: #2c3e50;
  transform: scale(1.2);
}

.homeb{
  color: #cf3be6;
  background-color: white;
  border:white solid;
  border-radius: 25px;
  padding-left: 15px;
  padding-right: 15px;
  cursor: pointer;
}


  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <a href="/">
    <button class="homeb">Go to Home</button>
  </a>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <section class="about-section">
      <p>
        In India, medical emergencies are often complicated by a critical information gap at the point of care. First responders and emergency room staff frequently treat unconscious, disoriented, or non-communicative patients without immediate access to their vital medical history.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our solution is to build a system where patients’ basic medical records are safely stored and can be instantly accessed in emergencies, while also spreading awareness about existing medical schemes.
      </p>
    </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 CareConnect. All Rights Reserved.</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    function openModal(id) {
      document.getElementById(id).style.display = "block";
    }
    function closeModal(id) {
      document.getElementById(id).style.display = "none";
    }
    window.onclick = function(event) {
      let modals = document.querySelectorAll(".modal");
      modals.forEach(m => {
        if (event.target === m) {
          m.style.display = "none";
        }
      });
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
